@startuml
' Sequence diagram: interaksi LINTAS-LAPIS Elixir <-> Kubernetes (komponen).
' Bagian atas = loop reconcile operator; bagian bawah = terminasi pod saat rolling update.
' Tema PlantUML/UML standar. Render: plantuml -tpdf seq_crosslayer.puml
title Interaksi lintas-lapis Elixir <-> Kubernetes

actor "kubelet" as K
participant "Operator\n(Elixir + kubectl)" as Op
participant "API server /\nDeployment" as API
participant "Pod aplikasi\n(ProbeHTTP, Shutdown,\nHandoff)" as Pod
participant "Pod survivor" as Surv

== Loop reconcile operator (tiap 5 detik) ==
Op -> API : kubectl get pods
API --> Op : daftar IP pod
Op -> Pod : HTTP GET /probe
Pod --> Op : {backlog, rate, T_c}
Op -> Op : Grace.compute(...)
Op -> API : kubectl patch\nterminationGracePeriodSeconds = g

== Terminasi pod (rolling update) ==
K -> Pod : SIGTERM
Pod -> Pod : preStop -> POST /drain\n(Shutdown.drain)
Pod -> Surv : handoff state (Horde)
alt handoff selesai sebelum grace
  Pod --> K : keluar bersih (tanpa kehilangan state)
else grace habis lebih dulu
  K -> Pod : SIGKILL (state sisa hilang)
end
@enduml
